聽聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T01:35:18.000Z","msg":"都已經係四五年前既事<br />\n到而家完全冇卡冇痛<br />\n希望冇惡化到掛 唔係都幾大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T01:43:55.000Z","msg":"好啦恭喜你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果遲D唔好彩再有問題<br />\n建議你睇口腔顩面專科搵意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bce7530c0bb62ef669a02dbcda8ac710ca7207","tid":518270,"uid":35421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾年 明顯下顎歪左 但冇痛 開合卡卡卡聲</blockquote><br />\n巴打唔去求醫既<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影響左儀容wor</blockquote><br />\nd  19 獸醫 一睇就話自己會好返  不過都多謝巴打你 會盡早求診"},{"pid":"3b48266b94786db0f8023cc7b7300e827a079f8d","tid":518270,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾年 明顯下顎歪左 但冇痛 開合卡卡卡聲</blockquote><br />\n巴打唔去求醫既<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影響左儀容wor</blockquote><br />\nd  19 獸醫 一睇就話自己會好返  不過都多謝巴打你 會盡早求診</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都慘受tmj之苦<br />\n而家睇左1個口腔顩面專科醫生<br />\n開藥食但態度mama<br />\n下星期睇第2個<br />\n<br />\n他日巴打你求醫有疑難<br />\n歡迎開post分享我一定share意見<br />\n祝福你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228450531a82552f853efc10d7f0c57a77bfb1b2","tid":518270,"uid":162806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"請問你地係睇邊個醫生？<br />\n我牙胶痛左個幾月 book左下個月睇牙醫<br />\n但係唔知岩唔岩"},{"pid":"3e553335276023e80b53ce0e17e965cf18c560c3","tid":518270,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"228450531a82552f853efc10d7f0c57a77bfb1b2","tid":518270,"uid":162806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"請問你地係睇邊個醫生？<br />\n我牙胶痛左個幾月 book左下個月睇牙醫<br />\n但係唔知岩唔岩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"睇一般牙醫只會開止痛藥消炎藥俾你<br />\n好彩既話你會醫得好<br />\n<br />\n唔好彩既話你要牙醫轉介睇專科<br />\n口腔顩面科<br />\n有可能整咬合板打類固醇或做手術黎醫"},{"pid":"44a52d782106be04ce671cbe68cefbe3efe81990","tid":518270,"uid":3439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾呢兩年有事<br />\n個口開到最大會俾個骹位kick住<br />\n<br />\n你地嘅問題有無影響耳仔？<br />\n我成日覺得耳道好似腫咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862f707f0ef80b75c3fc8743ee741da32a364c64","tid":518270,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾呢兩年有事<br />\n個口開到最大會俾個骹位kick住<br />\n<br />\n你地嘅問題有無影響耳仔？<br />\n我成日覺得耳道好似腫咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我耳仔就無<br />\n但塊面既肌肉就緊哂<br />\n包括眨眼feel到kick kick地<br />\n同經常頭痛"},{"pid":"739d430823fa7f415ff4bc480164528ab44990da","tid":518270,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T05:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾呢兩年有事<br />\n個口開到最大會俾個骹位kick住<br />\n<br />\n你地嘅問題有無影響耳仔？<br />\n我成日覺得耳道好似腫咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過提提你<br />\ntmj個關節正正就係耳朵前<br />\n所以好有機會影響埋"},{"pid":"b811b2b621d8b7354587b269ca10c7ca1d59b39f","tid":518270,"uid":78957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"無痛但牙骹左右咬合唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隻馬咁左右𡁻野。"},{"pid":"7e277bcb9af126bb076a26841f357449bb248c81","tid":518270,"uid":3439,"like